Cell["\<\
The full three-term symbolic identity is intentionally not sent to a single \
global FullSimplify call, because that was the slow and brittle part of the \
original exploratory notebook. The checks below keep the notebook responsive \
while still verifying the phase conventions and the final formula.\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"3e53cb2f-4bec-4da1-a1d9-f61edcf1411b"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"(*", " ", 
