Cell["\<\
Note: phi = Pi/3 makes the denominator 1 + 2 Cos[2 phi] vanish in this \
written form. The physical expression is obtained by taking the appropriate \
limit, as in the 60-degree special-case notebook.\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"3a669f6b-ece7-4463-9b19-810f9a8cdce4"]
